> The <emphasis
>&PostScript; Way of &kile;</emphasis
> can be turned off or on in
		<menuchoice
><guimenu
>Settings</guimenu
><guisubmenu
>Configure Kile...</guisubmenu>
		<guimenuitem
>LaTeX</guimenuitem
><guilabel
